    <group id="moreinfo">
        <text id="biodiversity_info">Biodiversity shows the environmental impact of the energy system. The higher the score, the more can animals and plants thrive in their natural habitats.</text>
        <text id="landuse_info">Land use shows how much land is used by the energy system. The smaller the indicator, the less impact from the energy system on land use.</text>
        <text id="pollution_info">CO2 emission shows how much greenhouse gas is released by the energy system. Lower emissions mean a lower impact on global warming.</text>
        <text id="support_info">Political support shows how popular your decisions are. The higher the support the more options in policy choices you have.</text>
        <text id="budget_info">The budget shows you how much money you have and can spend. At the beginning of each round, you receive new money.</text>
